                            <p><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i> Email: filmmedia@gmail.com</p>
                            <p><i class="fa fa-map"></i> Address: Kazan, st.Pushkina 32</p>
                            <p><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 8:00 - 20:00, Monday - Saturday, Sunday - closed</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
